# Google Sheets API Configuration
# Get your API key from: https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials

# Google Sheets API Key
VITE_GOOGLE_SHEETS_API_KEY=your_api_key_here

# Sheet ID for Services (extract from sheet URL)
# Example: https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/SHEET_ID/edit
VITE_SERVICES_SHEET_ID=your_services_sheet_id

# Sheet ID for Enquiries
VITE_ENQUIRIES_SHEET_ID=your_enquiries_sheet_id

# Setup Instructions:
# 1. Create a Google Cloud Project: https://console.cloud.google.com
# 2. Enable Google Sheets API
# 3. Create API credentials (API Key)
# 4. Create two Google Sheets:
#    - Services Sheet with columns: ID | Title | Image | Services (comma-separated) | Popular
#    - Enquiries Sheet with columns: Timestamp | Name | Phone | Email | Services
# 5. Get the Sheet IDs from the URLs
# 6. Copy this file to .env and fill in your values
